and why I'm leaving it.

5
00:00:56,423 --> 00:00:59,085
You can watch it later.
I was gonna mail it

6
00:00:59,192 --> 00:01:01,092
but now-- I'll just
give it to you now.

7
00:01:01,194 --> 00:01:03,025
Are you taking your VCR,
or did you leave that upstairs?

8
