I bought the VCR!
I'm taking my VCR!

9
00:01:05,900 --> 00:01:07,465
I bought—
It's the only thing I'm taking.

10
00:01:07,567 --> 00:01:09,933
What is that on top of the car?

11
00:01:11,037 --> 00:01:12,937
Is that a futon on top of the car?

12
