<i>It's only the latest in a series</i>

229
00:14:47,253 --> 00:14:51,280
<i>of anonymous acts of vandalism that began</i>
<i>last month during the Boston Aquarium's</i>

230
00:14:51,390 --> 00:14:53,960
<i>prolonged legal battle</i>
<i>with Lesser Construction.</i>

